  "text": "Throughout the data collection period, interviews were held at convenient times for participants. The researcher also ensured that participants felt comfortable to have a conversation about their experiences [CITATION_1] . The participants were more likely to have been comfortable communicating with the researcher who comes from the same cultural and linguistic background as they did.",
